  "metadata": {
    "description": "Workflow Designer assistant: graph editing with RAG, graph summary, units library, and conditional prompt lines. Inject (user message, graph, turn state, recent changes, last edit, follow-up context, previous turn, etc.) → RagSearch → Filter → FormatRagPrompt → Aggregate → Prompt → LLMAgent → ProcessAgent → ApplyEdits. Supports run_workflow, report, grep. Used by Flet chat via run_assistant_workflow()."
  }
}
